## Changed In This Local WIP

- Admin collection and discount tables no longer expose permanent disabled placeholder actions.
- Collection create/edit/check/open actions now respond through local state or real tenant links.
- Discount create/edit/duplicate/stop actions now respond in the admin UI.
- Payment setup wording was moved away from internal connection-state language toward buyer/business operation wording.
- App integration status wording now uses `受付前` instead of `未接続`.
- Checkout empty state now shows product, cart, and shipping recovery links instead of a single dead-end sentence.
- Checkout empty-state recovery is now covered by Playwright assertions for product, cart, and shipping links, with no fake order/payment success state.
- Order lookup and auth form confirmed states now show buyer recovery links instead of ending with text-only notices.
- Order lookup links to contact, shipping, and returns after valid input.
- Login/register links to mypage, orders, and favorites after valid input without claiming login or registration completion.
- TOP hero carousel transition duration aligned to `560ms`.
- Carousel movement completion now uses `transitionend` with a timeout fallback instead of relying only on a fixed timer.
- Hero images are preloaded through browser `Image` objects before interaction to reduce white flashes during slide changes.
- Carousel track now receives GPU-friendly rendering hints for smoother `translate3d` transitions.
- Active instruction files were updated to record this carousel-smoothness work.

